    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over the Horizon is a stylized action metroidvania with a focus on extreme speed, spectacular acrobatic combos, and motion-canceled</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>stylish action </strong>metroidvania with a focus on extreme speed and spectacular acrobatic combo action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/a498e7e4461d2a69adddfefc0a85b019.poster.avif?t=1735806550\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/a498e7e4461d2a69adddfefc0a85b019.webm?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/a498e7e4461d2a69adddfefc0a85b019.mp4?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Move faster and with style with Motion Cancellation.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enemies' attacks are powerful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dart between attacks with lightning speed and mercilessly wipe them out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/3b5ba2de36986d31c9ed281bb03cf0ec.poster.avif?t=1735806550\" width=482 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/3b5ba2de36986d31c9ed281bb03cf0ec.webm?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/3b5ba2de36986d31c9ed281bb03cf0ec.mp4?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Charge up your capacitor gauge and unleash powerful special moves.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trigger Motion Cancel and release the charged power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A single attack via the F-key is enough to grind enemies to powder.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/91f532020aed558f40ce7f4ef5660550.poster.avif?t=1735806550\" width=502 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/91f532020aed558f40ce7f4ef5660550.webm?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/91f532020aed558f40ce7f4ef5660550.mp4?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/73c544707c14529ab004a0954e46b227.poster.avif?t=1735806550\" width=502 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/73c544707c14529ab004a0954e46b227.webm?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/73c544707c14529ab004a0954e46b227.mp4?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Take on massive enemies.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/5efad70b6f1791e1e5915472744d0648.poster.avif?t=1735806550\" width=418 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/5efad70b6f1791e1e5915472744d0648.webm?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/5efad70b6f1791e1e5915472744d0648.mp4?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/041235adf085d1da71a1a2d1fa72cf46.poster.avif?t=1735806550\" width=526 height=236 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/041235adf085d1da71a1a2d1fa72cf46.webm?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001880/extras/041235adf085d1da71a1a2d1fa72cf46.mp4?t=1735806550\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
